@page "/g"
<PageTitle>G License Training Program</PageTitle>

<Transition>
<div class="course-bg g"></div>
<div class="course-page g">

  <section class="intro reveal">
    <h1>G License Training – Drive with Confidence and Safety</h1>
    <p>
      Getting your <b>Full G License</b> is the final step in Ontario’s graduated licensing system.  
      Our G course prepares you for both the road test and real-life driving —  
      giving you the skills, confidence, and awareness to stay safe on the road every day.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you’re upgrading from G2 or returning to driving after a break,  
      our professional instructors provide <b>individual coaching, advanced road training, and defensive driving techniques</b>  
      to help you pass your test on the first try.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="overview reveal">
    <h2>Program Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Training is designed to help you build real-world driving experience under the supervision of licensed instructors.  
      We focus on defensive habits, smooth vehicle control, and road awareness — not just passing the exam.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>City and highway driving practice</li>
      <li>Parallel and reverse parking</li>
      <li>Highway merging and lane changing</li>
      <li>Night and weather condition driving</li>
      <li>Emergency maneuvers and safe braking</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="requirements reveal">
    <h2>Requirements</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Valid Ontario G2 License</li>
      <li>Minimum age: 17 years old</li>
      <li>Medical fitness for driving</li>
      <li>Basic English communication skills</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="program-options reveal">
    <h2>Training Options</h2>

  <div class="tiers">
    <div class="tier">
      <h3>Standard G Package — <span>$400</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>3 in-car driving lessons (1 hour each)</li>
        <li>Highway and city driving practice</li>
        <li>Parking and test preparation</li>
        <li>Mock road test included</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Ideal for confident G2 drivers preparing for their final test.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tier premium">
      <h3>Advanced G Package — <span>$650</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>6 in-car driving lessons with professional instructor</li>
        <li>Full defensive driving and emergency training</li>
        <li>Vehicle provided for road test</li>
        <li>Flexible scheduling and weekend lessons</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Perfect for nervous or first-time drivers who want full confidence and road mastery.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>

  <section class="skills reveal">
    <h2>What You’ll Learn</h2>
    <div class="facts">
      <div><b>Highway Safety:</b> lane discipline, merging, maintaining safe distances</div>
      <div><b>Parking &amp; Manoeuvres:</b> reverse, parallel, uphill &amp; downhill parking</div>
      <div><b>Defensive Driving:</b> hazard recognition and collision avoidance</div>
      <div><b>Confidence Building:</b> practice real scenarios with instructor feedback</div>
    </div>
  </section>

