        </tr>
      </table>
  </section>

  <section class="faq reveal">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>How long does it take to get my G license?</h3>
      <p>Most students complete the training within 1–2 weeks depending on scheduling.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Do you provide a car for the test?</h3>
      <p>Yes. The Advanced Package includes a fully insured vehicle for your road test appointment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I book lessons on weekends?</h3>
      <p>Yes, weekend and evening lessons are available to fit your schedule.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is this program suitable for beginners?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Our instructors work with new and nervous drivers step-by-step to ensure safety and comfort.</p>
    </div>
